&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;East Kent Hospitals University NHS Foundation Trust is looking to establish its Medical Examiner (ME) service through the appointment of clinicians who have been registered practitioners with the GMC for at least 5 years. MEs will need to be able to undertake this role during the afternoons of the normal working week and will be required to work at either the WHH, Ashford or QEQM Margate sites. All applicants will need to have completed the eLearning modules on e-LFH.org before interview.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
